        <h1>Delete My Account</h1>
        
        <p>You can delete your Momentum account directly from the app. Deletion isn't revertable.</p>
        
        <h2>How to Delete Your Account</h2>
        
        <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <div class="step-text">Open the Momentum app</div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <div class="step-text">Go to the Profile tab</div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <div class="step-text">Click on Account</div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <div class="step-text">Select "Delete Account"</div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">5</div>
                <div class="step-text">Confirm the deletion</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Data Deleted</h2>
        <p>When you delete your account, the following data will be permanently removed:</p>
        <ul class="data-list">
            <li>Profile information (name, email, password)</li>
            <li>Custom workout programs</li>
            <li>Workout history</li>
            <li>Nutrition data</li>
            <li>Body measurements</li>
            <li>Coaching messages</li>
            <li>Personal records</li>
        </ul>
        
